txt.en: A Shakh-hai Overseer has shifted the morale of the battle!
Shakh-hai Overseer not defeated before 4/7/10 minutes have passed
The battle with the Shakh-hai is going poorly...
The tower winch has been destroyed

Three of Sarumans most feared Shakh-hai warriors have launched a surprise assault on the right flank of the wall. This trio of Shakh-hai overseers possess abilities that will strengthen the morale of their troops, while crushing and humiliting the champions of Helm's Deep in front of their own troops, broadly demoralizing them, unless the Shakh-hai can be stopped - and quickly.
A planning table has been destroyed

Shakh-hai overseers have entered into the deep and are assailing the wall from below. They plan to destroy any remnants of the Rohirrim commander's plans and supplies, allowing them to overtake the wall through sheer brute force.

Merit Rating

This quest starts with <rgb=#FFFF00>Full</rgb> Merit Rating.

<rgb=#FF0000>Major Merit Loss</rgb>
* Shakh-hai Overseer successfully uses a powerful ability
* Shakh-hai Overseer not defeated within 4 minutes
* 2nd Shakh-hai Overseer not defeated within 7 minutes
* 3rd Shakh-hai Overseer not defeated within 10 minutes
Defeat all three Shakh-hai Overseers within 10 minutes ([placeholder]/3)
